description:
Kick back and relax in this calm, stylish space where you can come straight from Suvarnabhumi Airport and easy access to the city centre

- ﻿﻿Easy to get a Bus, Taxi, Bike Taxi

- ﻿﻿Free laundry service! (Wash-Dry-Fold)
- 24 hour security services and CCTV﻿
